           MOVE   "PUTWINDOW"  TO  MCP-FUNC
           CALL   "ORCDBMAIN"          USING
                                       MCPAREA
                                       MCPDATA-REC
                                       SPA-AREA
           .
       900-PUT-WINDOW-EXT.
           EXIT.
